          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is a hybrid mattress?",
            "content": "<p>A hybrid mattress combines the responsive support of individually pocketed springs with the pressure-relieving comfort of memory foam — giving you the best of both technologies in a single mattress.<br/><br/>Every REM-Fit hybrid mattress is built around a core of individually wrapped pocket springs that move independently, so when your partner shifts position, you don't feel a thing. Above the springs sit layers of temperature-regulating memory foam engineered to distribute your weight evenly, easing pressure on your shoulders, hips and lower back.<br/><br/>Our range covers every sleep preference. The Pocket 1000 Hybrid offers an accessible entry point with 1,000 individual pocket springs and a medium-firm feel suited to most sleepers. The 4000 Ortho Elite provides firm orthopaedic support for back and joint pain sufferers, while the 5000 Lux Elite delivers a luxury sleep surface with advanced cooling gel technology for anyone who sleeps hot. For a softer, more enveloping feel, the 3000 Supreme Hybrid balances cushioned comfort with lasting support.<br/><br/>All our hybrid mattresses are available in single, double, king and super king sizes, come with free UK delivery, and are backed by a 100-night risk-free sleep trial and a 15-year guarantee.<br/><br/>Not sure which firmness suits you? Use our mattress comparison tool to find the right match for your sleep position and body type.</p>",
